{"type":null,"faqId":41628,"title":"When my phone is being charged, why does the screen always stay on?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s3{border::thin solid black;}\n.s4{font-size:10pt;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:0pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>Go to </span><span class=\"s1\">Developer options </span><span>to adjust this behavior. </span><span class=\"s1\">Developer options</span><span> is hidden by default.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>To show </span><span class=\"s1\">Developer options</span><span> in the settings menu, go to </span><span class=\"s1\">Settings</span><span> and touch </span><span class=\"s1\">About phone</span><span>.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>Touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Build number</span><span> 7 times in succession. A notification will appear saying you have entered Developer mode.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>Go back to </span><span class=\"s1\">Settings</span><span> and touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Developer options</span><span>. Clear the </span><span class=\"s1\">Stay awake</span><span> check box.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=140233\" style=\"width:2.4368055in;height:4.3319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s3\"> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=140234\" style=\"width:2.4333334in;height:4.327778in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s4\"> </span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=140235\" style=\"width:2.4375in;height:4.3326387in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=140236\" style=\"width:2.4375in;height:4.3326387in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0005947955\"><a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0005947956\"><a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0005947957\"><a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0005947958\"><a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0006492292\"><a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0006492293\"><a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0006523959\"></a></a></a></a></a></a></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=140237\" style=\"width:0.59375in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>The figures are for your reference only. The actual screens may vary.</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":244,"languageName":"mm","faqCode":"7088","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442207708000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-L01","visitedTimes":1,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":n